skill.dss.gui.main.title=Skill Manual
skill.dss.gui.main.body=This book contains entries for each skill you have learned.\n\n* Click on the bottom page corners or use the Page Down and Page Up keys to navigate forward or back.\n\n* Click on a category in the Table of Contents to jump to that page.\n\n* Shift-click a category to toggle it as an additional filter.\n\n* Click on a skill to view its description.\n\n* Right-click a skill to disable or re-enable it.
