skill.dss.armor_break.name=Sunder
skill.dss.armor_break.activation=Hold the attack key to charge up; once charged, the skill triggers automatically.
skill.dss.armor_break.description=Unleash a powerful and well aimed blow, inflicting full damage even against heavily armored opponents.
skill.dss.armor_break.tooltip=Unleash an armor-penetrating blow
skill.dss.back_slice.name=Shadowrush
skill.dss.back_slice.activation=[Sword] [Targeted]\nHold left or right and double-tap forward, then attack at the right time.
skill.dss.back_slice.description=Quickly circle around and hit 'em where it hurts!\n\nSome enemies are more vulnerable to attacks from behind, and many have a small chance to lose any equipped chest armor.\n\nHigher tiers of armor are harder to knock off. Each level of the Unbreaking enchantment reduces the chance by 5%%, whereas each level of Sharpness grants a +5%% bonus.\n\nNote that attacking too early, too late, or not from behind will only result in a standard attack.
