skill.dss.back_slice.info.chance=Disarmor Chance: %d%%
skill.dss.back_slice.tooltip=Attack an enemy's vulnerable backside
skill.dss.dash.name=Charge
skill.dss.dash.activation=Press the attack key while moving forward and blocking.
skill.dss.dash.description=Dash into an enemy at high speed, knocking the target back and inflicting minor damage. An effective dash requires sufficient space between you and your foe.\n\nEffects that increase your speed will increase the effective range, damage, and knockback.
skill.dss.dash.info.knockback=Base Knockback: %d
skill.dss.dash.info.min_range=Minimum Range: %s blocks
skill.dss.dash.tooltip=Dash attack knocks target back
skill.dss.dodge.name=Dodge
skill.dss.dodge.activation=Double-tap left or right to dodge in that direction.
skill.dss.dodge.description=Evading a blow takes more than quick feet - it's all about timing.\n\nDodge just as an attack is about to hit to increase your chances of evading the blow by up to 20%%.
skill.dss.dodge.info.bonus=Max Timing Bonus: +%d%%
skill.dss.dodge.info.chance=Base Dodge Chance: %d%%
skill.dss.dodge.tooltip=Actively evade incoming blows
skill.dss.ending_blow.name=Eviscerate
skill.dss.ending_blow.activation=[Targeted]\nAfter striking the same opponent two or more consecutive times, quickly double-tap forward and attack.
skill.dss.ending_blow.description=Throw an enemy off balance with consecutive blows and press the advantage with a ferocious attack to finish the enemy off.\n\nWhen used to finish off an enemy, bonus experience is awarded equal to the skill level of the player, plus an additional amount up to the final remaining health value of the slain foe.\n\nThis skill is not without risk, however; should the enemy survive, you will be flat-footed and vulnerable for the duration listed, or twice that time if your attack misses completely. Reckless use of this skill may very well result in an untimely demise.
skill.dss.ending_blow.tooltip=Finish off a vulnerable enemy
skill.dss.ending_blow.hud.activate=Finish him!
