skill.dss.rising_cut.name=Rising Cut
skill.dss.rising_cut.activation=[Sword]\nCrouch by pressing the sneak key, then jump and attack.
skill.dss.rising_cut.description=Fling an enemy into the air with an upward slash, following close behind for a possible second attack, in addition to the damage the target will take upon hitting the ground.
skill.dss.rising_cut.tooltip=Rising slash flings enemy upward
skill.dss.spin_attack.name=Pirouette
skill.dss.spin_attack.activation=Hold left and right to charge up; the first key determines the spin direction.
skill.dss.spin_attack.description=Useful when surrounded by enemies, the player spins around once in a circle, damaging all within range for the same amount as a standard attack.\n\nExhaustion is added at the start of each spin.
skill.dss.spin_attack.info.spins=Max Spins: %d
skill.dss.spin_attack.tooltip=Attacks all enemies in 360 degree arc
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.name=Whirlwind
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.activation=Quickly tap the attack key while Spin Attack is active to spin again.
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.description=This skill improves upon the basic Spin Attack, but only when at full health. Benefits include increased range and the ability to spin multiple times.
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.info.range=Bonus Range: %s blocks
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.info.spins=Bonus Spins: %d
skill.dss.super_spin_attack.tooltip=Attacks all enemies in 720+ degree arc
skill.dss.basic_technique.name=Focus
skill.dss.basic_technique.activation=Press the Z-Targeting key, default 'x', with a target in clear sight and within the maximum range.
skill.dss.basic_technique.description=The most basic technique revolves around awareness of one's opponents, always keeping an enemy in sight - this is referred to as "locking on."\n\nConsecutive strikes while locked on result in bonus "combo" damage, increasing as the combo grows.\n\nThe combo ends when one of the following occurs:\n - too much time passes between strikes\n - the player takes too much damage\n - the max combo size is reached
skill.dss.basic_technique.info.max=Max Combo Size: %d
skill.dss.basic_technique.info.tolerance=Damage Tolerance: %s
skill.dss.basic_technique.tooltip=Target foes and perform deadly combos
skill.dss.sword_beam.name=Razor Wind
skill.dss.sword_beam.activation=[Sword]\nCrouch by pressing the sneak key, then attack.
skill.dss.sword_beam.description=By slashing the air so quickly, the sword will unleash a powerful attack capable of striking foes from afar.\n\nDamage is a percentage of the sword's attack bonus; however, the ability's attack power diminishes with each target struck.\n\nIn order to perform such a technique, one must be at or near full health.
skill.dss.sword_beam.info.health=Max Missing Hearts: %f
skill.dss.sword_beam.tooltip=Shoot a powerful slash of razor sharp wind
skill.dss.sword_break.name=Deflect
skill.dss.sword_break.activation=Tap forward, forward, block just as the foe's strike is about to land. Shield is not required.
skill.dss.sword_break.description=A hard parry that greatly damages any weapon thus struck, while at the same blocking the attack. Like any parry, it must be well timed to be effective.\nKnockback effect increases slightly with skill level.
skill.dss.sword_break.info.durability=Damage: up to %d durability
skill.dss.sword_break.info.knockback=Knockback: %d
skill.dss.sword_break.tooltip=Damage or destroy an opponent's weapon
skill.dss.unknown.name=Unknown Skill
skill.dss.unknown.tooltip=Unlock this skill to view its description.
